<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
   <meta charset="UTF-8">
   <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
   <title>Event - Activation User</title>
   <style>
      body {
         font-family: "Inter", Arial, sans-serif;
         margin: 0;
         padding: 24px 12px;
         background-color: #f4f6fb;
         color: #1f2933;
      }

      .container {
         max-width: 600px;
         margin: 0 auto;
         background-color: #ffffff;
         border-radius: 16px;
         box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
         overflow: hidden;
         border: 1px solid #e3e8ee;
      }

      .header {
         background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4c6ef5, #83a4ff);
         color: #ffffff;
         padding: 32px;
         text-align: center;
      }

      .header h1 {
         margin: 0;
         font-size: 28px;
         letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      }

      .content {
         padding: 32px;
         line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .content p {
         margin: 0 0 16px;
         color: #4a5568;
      }

      .details {
         list-style: none;
         padding: 0;
         margin: 24px 0;
         border-top: 1px solid #edf2f7;
         border-bottom: 1px solid #edf2f7;
      }

      .details li {
         display: flex;
         justify-content: space-between;
         padding: 12px 0;
         font-size: 15px;
         color: #2d3748;
      }

      .details strong {
         color: #1a202c;
      }

      .button {
         display: inline-block;
         padding: 12px 28px;
         margin: 24px 0;
         color: #ffffff !important;
         background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4c6ef5, #6981ff);
         text-decoration: none;
         border-radius: 999px;
         font-weight: 600;
         letter-spacing: 0.3px;
         box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(76, 110, 245, 0.25);
      }

      .button:hover {
         background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3052d5, #4c6ef5);
      }

      .footer {
         background-color: #f4f6fb;
         color: #6b7280;
         padding: 20px;
         text-align: center;
         font-size: 12px;
      }

      .footer p {
         margin: 4px 0;
      }

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
         body {
            padding: 16px 8px;
         }

         .container {
            border-radius: 12px;
         }

         .content {
            padding: 24px;
         }
      }
   </style>
</head>
<body>
   <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
         <h1>Welcome!</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
         <p>Hello <%= username %>,</p>
         <p>
            Thank you for registering with us. Your account is ready—here are the details we have for you:
         </p>
         <ul class="details">
            <li><strong>Name: </strong> <%= fullName %></li>
            <li><strong>Email: </strong> <%= email %></li>
            <li><strong>Registration Date: </strong> <%= createdAt %></li>
         </ul>
         <p>Tap the button below to activate your account and start exploring events tailored for you.</p>
         <a href="<%= activationLink %>" class="button">Activate your account</a>
         <p>If you need any help, simply reply to this email—we are always ready to assist.</p>
         <p>Warm regards,<br/>ACARA Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
         <p>&copy; 2024 Event Management System. All rights reserved.</p>
         <p>Sent securely from ACARA HQ</p>
      </div>
   </div>
</body>
</html>
